          <msContents>
            <summary>Super genituram Francisci Mariae Advocati à Quinto Vercellensis, considerationes et disputationes per Petrum Advocatum ejus genitorem. Author's holograph MS. Illustrated by pen-drawn horoscopes. The work begins with a poetical dedication by the Author to his son, with whose future life, as forecast by astrological methods, this MS. is mainly concerned. At the end is a note of the births of four other children, the last in 1586, but the main work was completed in 1580.  Produced in Vercelli.</summary>
